Wait. It may not be a boy.

9
00:01:24,334 --> 00:01:25,502
It could be a girl.

10
00:01:26,711 --> 00:01:28,713
-Let's go.
-Do you feel better now?

11
00:01:28,797 --> 00:01:29,714
Are you okay?

12
00:01:41,017 --> 00:01:42,352
Hello?

13
00:01:42,435 --> 00:01:45,563
Is this Ms. Lee Si-eun?

14
00:01:46,731 --> 00:01:47,857
Yes.

15
00:01:47,941 --> 00:01:50,568
This is Nam Ga-bin.

16
00:01:52,153 --> 00:01:53,488
Yes.

17
00:01:53,571 --> 00:01:56,074
I heard you got into a fender bender.

18
00:01:56,157 --> 00:01:57,450
Are you okay?

19
00:01:57,534 --> 00:01:58,660
I am.

20
00:01:58,743 --> 00:02:00,829
I'd like to meet you in person.

21
00:02:01,663 --> 00:02:02,956
I think it's only right.

22
00:02:03,706 --> 00:02:07,794
So you can see how old I look
and justify your actions?

23
00:02:07,877 --> 00:02:09,337
Would you prefer not to?

24
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:12,423
What did Hae-ryun say?
Did he put you up to this?

25
00:02:12,507 --> 00:02:15,468
No. This is my idea.

26
00:02:17,929 --> 00:02:19,389
If you're uncomfortable,

27
00:02:21,015 --> 00:02:23,393
-I'll hang up.
-Where do you want to meet?

28
00:02:23,476 --> 00:02:26,938
Do you know a cafe called Deung
across from the Gangnam Department Store?

29
00:02:27,021 --> 00:02:28,064
