35
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:47,041
You're the first woman
to exude such an aura.

36
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:51,254
What about me?

37
00:02:51,337 --> 00:02:56,467
You've always looked lovely to me.

38
00:02:57,051 --> 00:02:58,177
Really?

39
