87
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,752
I worked like a dog.

88
00:06:18,628 --> 00:06:23,007
Only after joining my friend's law firm
did I finally get to live life.

89
00:06:23,674 --> 00:06:27,053
Then I got a gym membership, met you,

90
