122
00:08:44,899 --> 00:08:46,734
Like Daddy-Long-Legs.

123
00:08:48,027 --> 00:08:48,945
I mean…

124
00:08:50,446 --> 00:08:51,280
an oppa.

125
00:09:15,054 --> 00:09:16,389
I couldn't help myself.

126
00:09:18,099 --> 00:09:20,017
This may sound like an excuse,

127
00:09:20,851 --> 00:09:23,479
but you just looked too lovely in my eyes.

128
00:09:34,198 --> 00:09:35,658
In retrospect,

129
00:09:36,701 --> 00:09:39,620
I've had feelings for you
ever since we first met.

130
00:09:41,998 --> 00:09:43,374
Excuse me.

131
00:09:47,878 --> 00:09:50,256
-Enjoy your food.
-Thank you.

132
00:09:51,048 --> 00:09:52,300
Are you offended?

133
00:09:56,554 --> 00:09:59,515
