134
00:10:31,005 --> 00:10:33,132
I'm going to cheat on him at least once.

135
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:36,010
That'll help me forgive him and move on.

136
00:10:39,889 --> 00:10:41,557
I'm doing well.

137
00:10:42,683 --> 00:10:44,310
I'll visit you for Christmas.

138
00:10:45,770 --> 00:10:46,771
Goodbye.

139
00:10:50,274 --> 00:10:51,442
It's my sister-in-law.

140
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:08,751
I'm not doing this as a formality.

141
00:11:08,834 --> 00:11:10,086
I want to put this on you.

142
00:11:18,469 --> 00:11:19,595
This is how I feel.

143
00:11:20,429 --> 00:11:25,184
I had wanted to get a massive one,
but it would've been too heavy.

144
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:03,055
It fits me perfectly.

145
00:12:06,642 --> 00:12:08,644
But I didn't get you anything.

146
00:12:09,979 --> 00:12:14,150
That baby is my gift.
I bet it has grown big already.

147
00:12:20,322 --> 00:12:24,243
I told the sales clerk that you had
a similar size, and it was a size seven.

148
00:12:24,869 --> 00:12:25,911
Thank you.

149
00:12:27,621 --> 00:12:30,374
I'll wear it and keep it safe.

150
00:12:31,208 --> 00:12:34,879
I didn't buy my wedding ring myself.

151
00:12:35,629 --> 00:12:38,424
But I spent my own money on this.

152
00:12:40,593 --> 00:12:42,970
You always give me joy.

153
00:12:57,526 --> 00:13:02,364
Couldn't you have come out
with an umbrella since it's raining?

154
00:13:02,448 --> 00:13:05,201
Was it that hard to come out to the yard?

155
00:13:26,597 --> 00:13:27,640
Get lost.

156
00:13:29,892 --> 00:13:32,061
-"Get lost"?
-Unless you want a good beating.

157
00:13:34,021 --> 00:13:35,481
I'm speechless.

158
00:13:36,065 --> 00:13:37,733
You should know when to stop.

159
00:13:37,816 --> 00:13:39,568
You're one to talk.

160
00:13:39,652 --> 00:13:41,695
Look how brazen you are.

161
00:13:43,447 --> 00:13:44,448
Gosh, my back.

162
