My back.

163
00:13:50,913 --> 00:13:51,914
Gosh, it hurts.

164
00:14:01,423 --> 00:14:04,176
You're as strong as an ox.

165
00:14:06,387 --> 00:14:08,597
You could have broken my hip.

166
00:14:10,766 --> 00:14:13,060
