It stopped raining.

203
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:37,037
Whenever you need to see the doctor,

204
00:16:37,121 --> 00:16:38,956
make sure you go with my mom.

205
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:42,543
I'll tell her to keep you company, okay?

206
00:16:44,503 --> 00:16:45,504
And one more thing.

207
00:16:45,587 --> 00:16:48,924
I want to be there when you give birth.

208
00:16:49,008 --> 00:16:51,969
Call me immediately
when you get contractions.

209
00:16:52,052 --> 00:16:56,181
Even if the sky falls down,
I'll be by your side.

210
00:16:57,224 --> 00:16:59,226
I won't leave you to suffer alone.

211
00:16:59,309 --> 00:17:00,936
I'll hold your hand.

212
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:04,606
We need to welcome Bada together.

213
00:17:17,911 --> 00:17:20,122
I'll walk you to the door.

214
00:17:22,249 --> 00:17:25,002
Let's just say our goodbyes here.

215
00:17:32,134 --> 00:17:34,470
Do you still have the gloves I bought you?

216
00:17:36,930 --> 00:17:37,931
Of course.

217
00:17:44,688 --> 00:17:48,233
I carry them at all times
and wear them when I'm cold.

218
00:17:51,153 --> 00:17:52,988
What about the muffler I gave you?

219
00:17:53,072 --> 00:17:57,034
Of course, I still have it.
Should I send a photo of it tomorrow?

220
00:18:01,121 --> 00:18:02,039
I have a favor.

221
00:18:04,541 --> 00:18:05,834
Don't change your number.

222
00:18:06,335 --> 00:18:08,629
Even though I won't call you,

223
00:18:08,712 --> 00:18:11,090
knowing it will give me
a sense of comfort.

224
00:18:17,638 --> 00:18:18,931
Bada.

225
00:18:20,766 --> 00:18:22,434
Don't give your mom a hard time

226
00:18:23,185 --> 00:18:24,561
but be a good baby.

227
00:18:26,021 --> 00:18:30,025
I hope she'll be able to stomach
nutritious food soon.

228
00:18:30,984 --> 00:18:32,402
I will always be…

229
00:18:33,737 --> 00:18:38,659
by you and your mom's side.

230
00:19:27,875 --> 00:19:33,088
Promise me you'll stay healthy
until we meet again.

231
00:19:34,590 --> 00:19:35,799
And don't forget me.

232
00:21:38,005 --> 00:21:39,172
I'm going to be okay.

233
00:21:40,924 --> 00:21:42,134
I'm going to be okay.

234
00:21:43,218 --> 00:21:44,511
I'm going to be okay.

235
00:21:48,056 --> 00:21:50,183
This is going to end happily
no matter what.

236
00:21:51,059 --> 00:21:52,019
I won't cry.

237
00:22:01,903 --> 00:22:04,156
I love that you're here.

238
00:22:04,239 --> 00:22:06,325
I don't feel anxious
when I come home late.

239
00:22:06,408 --> 00:22:09,411
Why didn't you drink more?
Wasn't this gathering long overdue?

240
00:22:10,037 --> 00:22:11,538
Everyone wanted to

241
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:13,749
except for him.

242
00:22:14,374 --> 00:22:15,834
